text:
I Really Like You Piano - by Carly Rae Jepsen:
Attention: This Piano Cover Tutorial is not very easy!

You can learn step by step how to play "I Really Like You",
the new single by Carly Rae Jepsen on the piano.

If the song is too fast, please set down the speed
in the video-options at bottom-right of the video!

Perfect! Now you are able to play
"I Really Like You" by Carly Rae Jepsen on the piano!
